SQL_STMT_U.val: select debh_no,debh_hadr_name1,debh_hadr_name2,debh_hadr_address,debh_hadr_city,DEBH_TEL,decimal(sum(DEBB_ACTINVAH),13,2) as saldo, decimal(sum(DEBC_CREDITLIMIT),13,2) as klimit,decimal(sum(DEBC_FINANCELIMIT),13,2) as flimit, ktel from :1/debh cross join :1/debc cross join :1/debb left outer join (select DEBP_DEBH_NO,max(DEBP_TEL) as ktel from :1/debp group by debp_debh_no) as t2 on t2.DEBP_DEBH_NO=debH_no where debh_no=debc_debh and debc_admno=1 and debc_no=debb_debc_no group by debh_no,debh_hadr_name1,debh_hadr_name2,debh_hadr_address,debh_hadr_city,DEBH_TEL, ktel having sum(DEBB_ACTINVAH)<>0 order by debh_no
